Known Issues:
      In chungus, error handling sucks tremendously
      There are no software checks to make shore there are not any bugs
      When tab bars grow to long they go off the page
      When git graph commits on a single row grow too long the lines leading up to them and from them are indistinguishable
      the markdown parser sucks
      OpenRouter API key is only configurable by hand-editing chungus/api-key.js (not in settings)
      emptydesk.html is bare when all tabs are closed (no prompt to open Index or a new tab)
      Version history side panel compresses the graph before display so real branch topology is lost
